what is nfsgateway?


Please note that the HiveServer port will now change to 10010 if hive is using a binary transfer mode or 10011 if hive is using an http transport mode. You can use "netstat -anp | grep 1001[01]" to determine if the port is available on each of following HiveServer host(s): hdp-s2.hw.com. If the port is not available, the process using it must be terminated.

netstat -anp | grep 1001[01]

